flowchart TB
    subgraph U[User Space]
        PERF[perf CLI\nstat / record / report]
        PMU[pmu_monitor\ncustom C collector]
        APP[Python feature pipeline]
    end

    subgraph K[Kernel]
        PE[perf_event subsystem\nperf_event_open / read / mmap]
        BPF[eBPF programs\noptional filtering / aggregation]
        PROC[proc connector\nthread lifecycle events]
    end

    subgraph H[Event Sources]
        PMUHW[PMU counters\ninst_retired / branch_misses / iTLB]
        LBR[LBR branch stack\nrecent branch history]
        TP[tracepoints / sched events]
    end

    PERF --> PE
    PMU --> PE
    PMU --> PROC
    APP --> PMU

    PE --> PMUHW
    PE --> LBR

    BPF -. attach .-> PE
    BPF -. attach .-> TP

    PROC --> PMU
